   `D(ρ_n, σ_n'') / n ≥ R_1(ρ, ε) - R_1(ρ, ε) * ε_n + ε_n + o(1)` as `n → ∞`, where `σ_n''` is a specific sequence of states defined in terms of `ρ`, `σ`, `ε`, and `n`, and `R_1`, `R_2`, `ε_0` are constants from the Steins Lemma context. -/
